title: Nick de Louw
text:
Nick de Louw (born 9 February 1998) is a Dutch <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who plays for SV Someren.
Club career.
He made his professional debut in the <a href="Eerste%20Divisie">Eerste Divisie</a> for <a href="Helmond%20Sport">Helmond Sport</a> on 21 October 2016 in a game against <a href="De%20Graafschap">De Graafschap</a>.
